Description: # Tello-Python
        
        Control DJI Tello drone with python
        
        # Installation
        
            pip install tello-python
        
        # Examples
        
        \# 引入tello_python包，注意：这里是下划线_连接
        from tello_python import tello
        
        \# 初始化无人机对象
        drone = tello.Tello()
        
        \# 起飞
        drone.takeoff()
        
        \# 前进100cm
        drone.forward(100)
        
        \# 顺时针旋转90°
        drone.cw(90)
        
        \# 向左翻滚
        drone.flip('l')
        
        \# 打开视频流
        drone.streamon()
        
        \# 降落
        drone.land()
        
        更多命令请参考源码tello.py文件内的方法及注释
